ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of PATRICIA JANET MELLA of Stratford, Prince Edward Island, to be a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of William Charles Rooney; and appointment of PATRICIA JANET MELLA, to be part-time Vice-Chairperson of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority.
